never change. Accept it.

138
00:07:11,089 --> 00:07:14,301
You'll be a whole lot
happier that way.

139
00:07:14,301 --> 00:07:18,222
Ha, ha, ha, heh, heh, ha!

140
00:07:18,222 --> 00:07:20,724
Jerk. You'd better
stop laughing at me...

141
00:07:20,724 --> 00:07:23,101
I'm getting stronger
just wait you'll--

142
00:07:26,063 --> 00:07:29,191
Yeah! Good one, but what
about the footwork, Daimonji?!

143
00:07:29,191 --> 00:07:30,734
No wait! I give up!

144
00:07:30,734 --> 00:07:33,570
Daimonji kick!

145
00:07:33,570 --> 00:07:36,615
