151
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:56,414
Let's go grab some grub.

152
00:07:56,414 --> 00:07:57,915
Hey, don't forget your chores.

153
00:07:57,915 --> 00:07:59,417
Get those floors squeaky clean.

154
00:07:59,417 --> 00:08:01,669
Yeah, and scrub
those toilets too!

155
00:08:01,669 --> 00:08:03,379
See ya.

156
00:08:06,215 --> 00:08:08,759
